Name: Feelin
About the game: Feelin is a Co-building Open World All constructions shared by all players!! First, let's go collect some material items. Wooden resources, stones, fabric roofs drops around. Use Land Coins to purchase land sections. Yes, you can own a section of land in the open world. Compared to sandboxes with 1m voxels, you can build more detailed buildings at 10cm interval grids. Also enjoy gardening, let's make the green land together. Here is beautiful green and water world. Everything is cloud-saved and infinitely wide, just like the web. It's a long-lasting, long-running game. Let's start building open world with us, Feeliners!
